              "coded_information": [
                "HE3SP"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Two arrays of 3He proportional counters with",
                "diameters 125 and 190 mm respectively, are imbedded",
                "in a cylindrical polyethylene moderator 405 mm in",
                "diam. and 420 mm in length, h, around a centra] hole",
                "76 mm in diam.. The first array consists of six 10-atm",
                "counters of the LND type and the second one - of twelve",
                "SNM-18 3-atm counters. Each counter is served by its",
                "own preampiifier and discriminator.",
                "The detector efficicncy in registering neutrons for",
                "these two cases was 28.4+-0.6% and 34.2+-0.8%,",
                "rcspectively."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SIBAR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The flux of neutrons emitted by the Ti-T target",
                "of the neutron generator was measured by registering",
                "particles  with the Si-Au surface-bamer detector."
              ]
            }
          ],
